{"name": "odoo14-addon-project-milestone", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-project-milestone", "version": "14.0.1.4.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/project", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Project Milestones", "upload_time": 1726121764}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fproject-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/project\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/project/tree/14.0/project_milestone\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/project-14-0/project-14-0-project_milestone\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/project&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-patrickrwilson: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/patrickrwilson.png?size=40px\n    :alt: patrickrwilson\n    :target: https://github.com/patrickrwilson\n    ```\n---\n\n# Project Milestones\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:14320ac6f6365c05081ef94abb3cce409d7508eaf9eb54e1b29de64d4ed7e13f\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module provides a project milestones on projects.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module, you need to:\n\n1. Have Manager rights for Project group to edit projects.\n2. On the project form, set the \"Use Milestones\" option to enable milestones for the project.\n3. Add the milestones to the project via the milestone tab on the project form.\n4. Use 'Milestone Required' field to make milestone selection on tasks mendatory.\n5. Tasks will show a \"Milestone\" where you can set tasks into the proper milestone.\n6. You also have the group by \"Milestones\" for task views.\n7. All the subtask will inherit the milestone from parent task (if assigned)\n\n## Changelog\n\n### 14.0.1.0.0\n\n- Initial release\n\n### 14.0.1.1.0\n\n- New features added\n  : 1. Subtask inherit the milestones from parent task\n    2. 'Milestone Required' field is added on project\n    3. Milestone can be assigned directly from Task Kanban\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/project/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/project/issues/new?body=module:%20project_milestone%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Patrick Wilson\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Patrick Wilson \\<<mailto:patrickraymondwilson@gmail.com>>\n\n- [Ooops](https://www.ooops404.com):\n\n  - Ashish Hirpara\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-patrickrwilson }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/project](https://github.com/OCA/project/tree/14.0/project_milestone) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.project_milestone.models.project", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.project_milestone.models.project.Project", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.project_milestone.models.project.Project._onchange_use_milestones", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.project_milestone.models.project.Project.copy", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "default", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.project_milestone.models.project.Project._link_tasks_to_milestones", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.project_milestone.models.project.Project._find_equivalent_milestone", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "milestone", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.project_milestone.models.project.Projec